import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

import Dashboard from './components/Dashboard'
import Layout from './layout/Layout'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Layout>
        <Switch>
          <Route path='/'>
            <Dashboard />
          </Route>
        </Switch>
      </Layout>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
